  m_Name: Start_Dialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogData
  lines:
  - Perfect! Thanks for getting the small robot builder up and running.
  - The builder can now produce infinite copies of itself for us to program, pretty
    cool right?
  - Now if you wouldn't mind, are you able to help us program and teach them how
    to do various jobs and tasks? I'll show you where you can learn it all.
